{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# 🔒 Private Endpoint Limit Helper\n\nThis workbook helps you identify Virtual Networks (VNETs) approaching their Private Endpoint (PE) limits and drill down into the resources consuming those endpoints.\n\n| Scope | Limit |\n|---|---|\n| Private Endpoints per VNET | **1,000** |\n| Private Endpoints across peered VNETs (hub-spoke) | **4,000** |\n| Private Endpoints per subscription | **64,000** |\n\n> **Source**: [Azure subscription and service limits – Private Link limits](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-resource-manager/management/azure-subscription-service-limits#private-link-limits)"
      },
      "name": "Header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0001-0001-000000000001",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Subscriptions",
            "type": 6,
            "isRequired": true,
            "multiSelect": true,
            "quote": "'",
            "delimiter": ",",
            "value": [
              "value::all"
            ],
            "typeSettings": {
              "additionalResourceOptions": [
                "value::all"
              ],
              "includeAll": true,
              "showDefault": false
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0001-0001-000000000002",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "WarningThreshold",
            "label": "Warning Threshold (%)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": "70",
            "typeSettings": {
              "paramValidationRules": [
                {
                  "regExp": "^[0-9]{1,3}$",
                  "match": true,
                  "message": "Enter a number between 0 and 100"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "a1b2c3d4-0001-0001-0001-000000000003",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "CriticalThreshold",
            "label": "Critical Threshold (%)",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": "90",
            "typeSettings": {
              "paramValidationRules": [
                {
                  "regExp": "^[0-9]{1,3}$",
                  "match": true,
                  "message": "Enter a number between 0 and 100"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 1,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
      },
      "name": "GlobalParameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "tab-overview",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "📊 Overview",
            "subTarget": "overview",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-hubspoke",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "🌐 Hub-Spoke Analysis",
            "subTarget": "hubspoke",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-vnet-detail",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "🔍 VNET Detail",
            "subTarget": "vnetdetail",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-by-resource-type",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "📦 By Resource Type",
            "subTarget": "byresourcetype",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "tab-by-subscription",
            "cellValue": "selectedTab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "📋 By Subscription",
            "subTarget": "bysubscription",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "TabNavigation"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Overview — Private Endpoints per VNET\n\nThis view shows all VNETs ranked by the number of Private Endpoints, with usage percentage relative to the **1,000 PE per VNET** limit. Use the thresholds above to customize warning/critical levels."
            },
            "name": "OverviewDescription"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| extend vnetId = strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourceGroups/', peRG, '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/', vnetName)\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by vnetId, vnetName, peSubId, peRG\r\n| extend PctUsed = round(todouble(PECount) / 1000.0 * 100, 1)\r\n| extend Status = case(\r\n    PctUsed >= {CriticalThreshold}, '🔴 Critical',\r\n    PctUsed >= {WarningThreshold}, '🟡 Warning',\r\n    '🟢 OK')\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resourcecontainers\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions'\r\n    | project peSubId = subscriptionId, SubName = name\r\n) on peSubId\r\n| project Status, vnetName, SubName, peRG, PECount, PctUsed, Remaining = 1000 - PECount, vnetId\r\n| order by PECount desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Top VNETs by Private Endpoint Count (Limit: 1,000 per VNET)",
              "exportFieldName": "vnetId",
              "exportParameterName": "SelectedVnetId",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Status",
                    "formatter": 1
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PECount",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 1000,
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "compositeBarSettings": {
                        "labelText": "",
                        "columnSettings": []
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PctUsed",
                    "formatter": 3,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 100,
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    },
                    "numberFormat": {
                      "unit": 1,
                      "options": {
                        "style": "decimal",
                        "maximumFractionDigits": 1
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Remaining",
                    "formatter": 1
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "vnetId",
                    "formatter": 13,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Resource",
                      "showIcon": true
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 1000,
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "PECount",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ],
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "Status",
                    "label": "Status"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "vnetName",
                    "label": "VNET Name"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "SubName",
                    "label": "Subscription"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "peRG",
                    "label": "Resource Group"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PECount",
                    "label": "PE Count"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PctUsed",
                    "label": "% Used"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Remaining",
                    "label": "Remaining"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "vnetId",
                    "label": "VNET Resource"
                  }
                ]
              },
              "sortBy": [
                {
                  "itemKey": "PECount",
                  "sortOrder": 2
                }
              ]
            },
            "name": "OverviewGrid"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by vnetName\r\n| order by PECount desc\r\n| take 20",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Top 20 VNETs by PE Count",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "vnetName",
                "yAxis": [
                  "PECount"
                ],
                "showLegend": true,
                "ySettings": {
                  "numberFormatSettings": {
                    "unit": 0,
                    "options": {
                      "style": "decimal",
                      "useGrouping": true
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            "name": "OverviewChart"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| summarize TotalPEs = count()\r\n| extend Title = 'Total Private Endpoints'",
              "size": 3,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Title",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "rightContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "TotalPEs",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "TileTotalPEs"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by vnetName\r\n| summarize VNETsWithPEs = count()\r\n| extend Title = 'VNETs with PEs'",
              "size": 3,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Title",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "rightContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "VNETsWithPEs",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "TileVNETCount"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by vnetName\r\n| where PECount >= ({WarningThreshold} * 10)\r\n| summarize AtRiskVNETs = count()\r\n| extend Title = strcat('VNETs >= ', {WarningThreshold}, '% Used')",
              "size": 3,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Title",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "rightContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "AtRiskVNETs",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "redDark"
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "TileAtRiskVNETs"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by vnetName\r\n| summarize MaxPEsInSingleVNET = max(PECount)\r\n| extend Title = 'Max PEs in single VNET'",
              "size": 3,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Title",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "rightContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "MaxPEsInSingleVNET",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  }
                },
                "showBorder": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "25",
            "name": "TileMaxPEs"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "selectedTab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "overview"
      },
      "name": "OverviewGroup"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Hub-Spoke Analysis — Peered VNET Private Endpoint Aggregation\n\nIn hub-spoke architectures, the combined PE count across peered VNETs is limited to **4,000**. This view shows each peered VNET with the **aggregated** PE count (own + all peers) compared against the 4,000 limit.\n\n> **How it works**: For each VNET that has peerings, the query sums its own PE count plus the PE count of every directly peered VNET. The group total is what matters for the 4,000 limit.\n\n> **Columns**: **Own PEs** = PEs in this VNET only | **Peer PEs** = sum of PEs across all peered VNETs | **Group Total** = Own + Peer (compared against 4,000)"
            },
            "name": "HubSpokeDescription"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "// Step 1: Start from all VNETs that have peerings\r\nresources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/virtualnetworks'\r\n| where array_length(properties.virtualNetworkPeerings) > 0\r\n| extend localVnetId = tolower(id)\r\n| extend localVnetName = name\r\n| mv-expand peering = properties.virtualNetworkPeerings\r\n| extend remoteVnetId = tolower(tostring(peering.properties.remoteVirtualNetwork.id))\r\n| extend remoteName = extract(@'/virtualNetworks/(.+)$', 1, remoteVnetId)\r\n// Step 2: Get PE count for each remote peer\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resources\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n    | extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n    | parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n    | extend vnetId = tolower(strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourceGroups/', peRG, '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/', vnetName))\r\n    | summarize RemotePECount = count() by vnetId\r\n) on $left.remoteVnetId == $right.vnetId\r\n// Step 3: Aggregate peer PE counts per local VNET\r\n| summarize PeerPETotal = sum(coalesce(RemotePECount, 0)), PeeredVNETs = make_set(remoteName), PeeringCount = count() by localVnetId, localVnetName\r\n// Step 4: Get own PE count\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    resources\r\n    | where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n    | extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n    | parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n    | extend vnetId = tolower(strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourceGroups/', peRG, '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/', vnetName))\r\n    | summarize OwnPECount = count() by vnetId\r\n) on $left.localVnetId == $right.vnetId\r\n| extend OwnPECount = coalesce(OwnPECount, 0)\r\n| extend GroupPETotal = OwnPECount + PeerPETotal\r\n| extend Limit = 4000\r\n| extend PctUsed = round(todouble(GroupPETotal) / 4000.0 * 100, 1)\r\n| extend Status = case(\r\n    PctUsed >= {CriticalThreshold}, '🔴 Critical',\r\n    PctUsed >= {WarningThreshold}, '🟡 Warning',\r\n    '🟢 OK')\r\n| extend Remaining = 4000 - GroupPETotal\r\n| project Status, localVnetName, OwnPECount, PeerPETotal, GroupPETotal, Limit, PctUsed, Remaining, PeeringCount, PeeredVNETs, localVnetId\r\n| order by GroupPETotal desc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "Peered VNETs — Aggregated PE Count (Own + Peers) vs 4,000 Limit",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Status",
                    "formatter": 1
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "localVnetId",
                    "formatter": 13,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "Resource",
                      "showIcon": true
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "GroupPETotal",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 4000,
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PctUsed",
                    "formatter": 3,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 100,
                      "palette": "greenRed"
                    },
                    "numberFormat": {
                      "unit": 1,
                      "options": {
                        "style": "decimal",
                        "maximumFractionDigits": 1
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "PeeredVNETs",
                    "formatter": 7,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "linkTarget": "CellDetails",
                      "linkLabel": "📋 View VNETs",
                      "linkIsContextBlade": true
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "rowLimit": 500,
                "filter": true,
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "Status",
                    "label": "Status"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "localVnetName",
                    "label": "VNET Name"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "OwnPECount",
                    "label": "Own PEs"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PeerPETotal",
                    "label": "Peer PEs"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "GroupPETotal",
                    "label": "Group Total"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Limit",
                    "label": "Limit"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PctUsed",
                    "label": "% Used"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Remaining",
                    "label": "Remaining"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PeeringCount",
                    "label": "Peerings"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "PeeredVNETs",
                    "label": "Peered VNETs"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "localVnetId",
                    "label": "VNET Resource"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "HubSpokeGrid"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/virtualnetworks'\r\n| mv-expand peering = properties.virtualNetworkPeerings\r\n| extend localVnet = name\r\n| extend localVnetId = tolower(id)\r\n| extend remoteVnetId = tolower(tostring(peering.properties.remoteVirtualNetwork.id))\r\n| extend remoteName = extract(@'/virtualnetworks/(.+)$', 1, remoteVnetId)\r\n| extend peeringState = tostring(peering.properties.peeringState)\r\n| extend peeringName = tostring(peering.name)\r\n| project localVnet, remoteName, peeringState, peeringName, localVnetId, remoteVnetId\r\n| order by localVnet asc",
              "size": 0,
              "showAnalytics": true,
              "title": "All VNET Peering Relationships",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "peeringState",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Connected",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}{1}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "localVnetId",
                    "formatter": 5
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "remoteVnetId",
                    "formatter": 5
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "localVnet",
                    "label": "Local VNET"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "remoteName",
                    "label": "Remote VNET"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "peeringState",
                    "label": "Peering State"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "peeringName",
                    "label": "Peering Name"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "PeeringRelationships"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "selectedTab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "hubspoke"
      },
      "name": "HubSpokeGroup"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## VNET Detail — Drill Down into Private Endpoints\n\nSelect a VNET below to see all Private Endpoints deployed in it, their target resources, subnets, and connection status."
            },
            "name": "VnetDetailDescription"
          },
          {
            "type": 9,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
              "parameters": [
                {
                  "id": "a1b2c3d4-0002-0002-0002-000000000001",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "SelectedVnet",
                  "label": "Select VNET",
                  "type": 2,
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| extend vnetId = strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourceGroups/', peRG, '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/', vnetName)\r\n| summarize PECount = count() by vnetId, vnetName\r\n| order by PECount desc\r\n| project value = vnetId, label = strcat(vnetName, ' (', PECount, ' PEs)'), selected = false",
                  "crossComponentResources": [
                    "{Subscriptions}"
                  ],
                  "typeSettings": {
                    "additionalResourceOptions": [],
                    "showDefault": false
                  },
                  "queryType": 1,
                  "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
                }
              ],
              "style": "pills",
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources"
            },
            "name": "VnetSelector"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "resources\r\n| where type =~ 'microsoft.network/privateendpoints'\r\n| extend subnetId = tostring(properties.subnet.id)\r\n| parse kind=regex subnetId with '/subscriptions/' peSubId '/resourceGroups/' peRG '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/' vnetName '/subnets/' subnetName\r\n| extend vnetId = strcat('/subscriptions/', peSubId, '/resourceGroups/', peRG, '/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/', vnetName)\r\n| where vnetId =~ '{SelectedVnet}'\r\n| summarize PECount = count()\r\n| extend Title = 'Private Endpoints'",
              "size": 4,
              "queryType": 1,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.resourcegraph/resources",
              "crossComponentResources": [
                "{Subscriptions}"
              ],
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "Title",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "leftContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "PECount",
                  "formatter": 12,
                  "formatOptions": {
                    "palette": "auto"
                  },
                  "numberFormat": {
